data.description: Country living on paved roads.  This well maintained 3 bed 2 bath home sits on 10 acres of beautiful Bermuda.  The lawn is lush and the fields provide great grazing or hay, two cuts per year.  The barn previously had horse stalls, and there is a separate fenced area to keep livestock or horses separated.  Nice back deck to relax in the evening and capture those beautiful Oklahoma sunsets.  There is a storm shelter located in the backyard for ease of access.  The carport has electric and has been walled and a separate storage with separate electrical panel is located in the rear, perfect for a workshop or storage.  The home has many updates.  The master bath has a beautiful restored clawfoot tub perfect for soaking after a long days work.  New roof, decking, gutters, insect repellant window screens in 2019. New flooring in living 2021, new master bed carpet and hotwater heater in 2023.
